## Project Structure

```
apps/
  api/           ← Go API (runtime: go {{.GoVersion}})
    main.go      ← Entry point, graceful shutdown
    bootstrap/   ← Module initialization (init order matters)
    config/      ← Env-based config, loaded once at startup
    api/         ← HTTP router, middleware, handlers
  web/           ← Next.js frontend (TypeScript, Tailwind)
infra/
  docker-compose.yaml  ← Local dev infrastructure
Makefile         ← All common tasks
.env.example     ← Required environment variables
.modkit.yaml     ← Module registry manifest
```

